metadata.name: The Block
metadata.description:
Chapter 4:  
The Block  
May, 2022 - Planet "Earth"

A old message from the Ancient Astronauts was found recently talking about a "mysterious cube" (original word also interpreted and adopted as "block" by  the Mr.Swe's Labs recently). 
It seems the block is moving and fluctuating in the middle of a strong magnetic field.  
External and unknown forces are acting, destabilizing the original trajectory. 

We are going to investigate also the message and the frequencies it was spreading along the way.

Early observations suggests are positive vibrations and we need to go in depth to understand the further implication of it.

Nobody know when the block starts his journey, only few in the universe know what message his carrying.
